        {
            "title": "唐家成：488家企業正排隊上市　審核過程絕無鬆懈",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港交所(00388)主席唐家成出席新春開市儀式致辭時表示，期望港股市場氣氛能一直延續，提到今年以來已有24隻新股上市，集資額超過870億元，現時有488家企業排隊上市。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">唐家成說，數量提升的同時，審核過程都絕無鬆懈，確保香港持續是備受認可的高質素市場。證券市場亦繼續創出佳績，去年的日均成交額破紀錄近2500億元，但今年1月日均成交額逾2780億元，最近有交易日更逾3000億元，反映各項提升流動性措施方案是正確和成效明顯。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">他說，今年會全力推進各項工作，包括公布提升上市制度和T+1的諮詢文件，第二階段收窄買賣價差亦計劃在年中落實。今年會繼續與各業界持份者緊密合作，致力令市場更具競爭力和高效。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15673165-%e5%94%90%e5%ae%b6%e6%88%90%ef%bc%9a488%e5%ae%b6%e4%bc%81%e6%a5%ad%e6%ad%a3%e6%8e%92%e9%9a%8a%e4%b8%8a%e5%b8%82%e3%80%80%e5%af%a9%e6%a0%b8%e9%81%8e%e7%a8%8b%e7%b5%95%e7%84%a1%e9%ac%86%e6%87%88-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/02/20260213_FI_source-web_00388_TONG_FB.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-20 10:06:45",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "港股紅盤低開48點  阿里百度領跌  MINIMAX續升",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股恒生指數馬年開市紅盤低開48點或0.18%，報26657點 ; 恒生科技指數開跌36點或0.69%，報5330點 ; 恒生國企指數開跌17點或0.19%，報9052點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">大市成交51.6億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"智譜與MiniMax的上市衝刺，成為觀察產業走向的風向標。\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2025/12/20251227_blog_source_web_blog4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"智譜與MiniMax的上市衝刺，成為觀察產業走向的風向標。\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2025/12/20251227_blog_source_web_blog4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">智譜與MiniMax的上市衝刺，成為觀察產業走向的風向標。</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">阿里巴巴(09988)跌3.03%，報150元 ; 百度(09888)跌2.98%，報133.5元。另一AI概念MINIMAX(00100)升5.43%，報893元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">速騰聚創(02498)預告虧損收窄，開升4.42%，報35.92元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">騰訊(00700)跌0.28%，報531.5元，成交居首 ; 攜程(09961)升1.76%，報427.2元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">寧德(03750)升1.22%，報538元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">創科(00669)跌2.69%，報119.5元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15673127-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e7%b4%85%e7%9b%a4%e4%bd%8e%e9%96%8b48%e9%bb%9e-%e9%98%bf%e9%87%8c%e7%99%be%e5%ba%a6%e9%a0%98%e8%b7%8c-minimax%e7%ba%8c%e5%8d%87",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20240420240415_FI_source-web_HKSTOCK.png.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-20 09:35:52",
