            "title": "即月期指開跌60點   高水34點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">即月期指開報26740，跌60點或0.224%，高水34點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">科指期貨開報5368，跌119點或0.35%，平水。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">國指期貨開報9084，跌12點或0.13%，高水14點。</p>\n</div>",
